- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the platform supports analysis of synchronous transition systems.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the platform supports probabilistic evaluation of Fault Trees.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the platform deals with safety analysis, which can be related to security.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also less likely but possible as the platform involves model-based analysis, which can be related to programming languages.
